  "title": "Service Crew (Karaoke) – Night Shift",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Locations:</strong> Downtown East / Seletar Mall / Suntec City / Toa Payoh / Punggol<br />💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> $2,100 – $3,000 (inclusive of night shift allowance up to $400/month)<br />🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> 44 hours/week</p><ul><li><p>Night Shift: <strong>6:30pm – 3:30am</strong> or <strong>4:30pm – 1:30am</strong></p></li><li><p><em>Minimum 4 hours OT/week required</em></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Provide excellent customer service in a karaoke environment</p></li><li><p>Take orders, serve food/drinks, and assist guests with room needs</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and restock supplies</p></li><li><p>Support crowd flow during peak hours</p></li><li><p>Uphold safety, hygiene, and service standards</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Able to work night shifts</p></li><li><p>Friendly, customer-oriented & a strong team player</p></li><li><p>Experience in F&B/events is advantageous but <strong>training provided</strong></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Benefits</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Quarterly Performance Bonus</p></li><li><p>Referral Bonus</p></li><li><p>Medical & Dental Benefits</p></li><li><p>Birthday Ang Pao</p></li><li><p>Company Transport</p></li><li><p>Incremental Annual Leave (from 10 days)</p></li><li><p>Career Advancement Opportunities<br /></p><p><br />EA License No: 23C1703</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p></li></ul>",
